    "# Module 2: Relational Database Architecture & Advanced Analytics Portfolio\n",
    "**Author:** Rakshit Gupta  \n",
    "**Objective:** Construct standard database schemas, initialize enterprise constraints, map entity connections via explicit relational constraints, and evaluate analytics challenges across five specialized assessment blocks."
